Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind stopped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we should be rushing\Nstraight for Little Garden, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're temporarily stopped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is running out as we speak, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we need to get to Alabasta\Nas soon as possible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's fish! Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anyone seen the bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bait? Oh, the stuff in there? I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it?! Those were bugs, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? They taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?! We can't fish now\Nthat you've eaten our bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't catch anything with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? We can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That sounds okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, you! Come here!\N--Get back here, bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you guys! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can't you guys be\Na little worried, at least?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nami-san is lovely\Nwhen she's angry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone with a\N30 million-Berry bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't seem that\Nterrible of a person at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it might be hard to imagine,\Nbut he's beaten many big names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, the fishman who was\Nbent on ruling the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Fleet Commodore, Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuro, an unknown pirate\Nnotorious for his cunning methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A navy freak who wields a huge axe-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Axe-Hand Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe-Hand Morgan?\NI've heard of him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's a navy captain\Nwho's feared in the East Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for his overwhelming domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying he beat even him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The old axe-hand guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, I wonder what\Nthat guy with him is up to now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's still\Nat that navy base...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! His name's Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Try Hard, Coby!\NCoby-Meppo's Struggles in the Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sub-Lieutenant!\NPreparations for departure are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! How are you?\NIt's me! Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we parted ways back then,\NI've worked my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were plenty of hardships,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I've achieved my\Ndream of being a navy officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Hell, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\NQuit screwing around, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up!\N--Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep, you idiot chore boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chore Boy"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Luffy-san,\NI'm now working at the navy base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Morgan's son Helmeppo-san\Nwas given chore duty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Quit slackin' off!\N--Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chore boys! Wash the windows\Nwhen you're done cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget to\Nclean up in the mess hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! What about our meal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're obviously not\Ngonna finish before lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat after\Nyou've finished everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! But I'm starving to death here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo! Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both aware neither of you\Nwere qualified to join the navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet you were given special\Npermission to join as chore boys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you let us join, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Of course! If there's\Nanything I can do, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... just making sure you realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll also be honored to do your laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you an idiot?!\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to go out of\Nyour way for even more work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we are chore boys,\Nafter all! Okay! Work! Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna work that badly,\Nyou can do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Two! Three! Four!\NOne! Two! Three! Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this. Forget Coby--\Nwhy do I hafta be a chore boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I wish I could go back to then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-sama. Your cocoa, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Are you trying to scald me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir! I-I'm very sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Helmeppo-sama, only son of\Nthe great Navy Captain Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Helmeppo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, things were good back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is all\Nthat Straw Hat's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stripped Dad of his\Nposition as a navy captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of Straw Hat that\NI'm stuck doing this crap now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!\NDon't touch me all friendly-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But I wanted to tell\Nyou something, as a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?! Why would\Nme and you be friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are both chore boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the kind of guy who\Ndoes chores in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it hadn't been for Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to blame Luffy-san\Nfor everything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blaming your fate on others\Nwon't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree that's\Nthe sign of a weakling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, you lived your\Nlife using your father's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from here on out,\Nwe need to face forward
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and search for our dreams on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will be a navy officer\Nwho cracks down on bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wimp like you, being a navy\Nofficer?! That'll never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing how Luffy-san lives\Nhis life, I made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be it, so if I die\Nfighting for that, that's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to be like Luffy-san\Nand put my life on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to strive for my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see? So let's both\Nwork hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, lecturing me?! Since when\Nare you that high and mighty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly learn\Nfrom that despicable Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk bad about Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't said anything that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that were true,\Nyou still piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san!\NPlease come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're anyone to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this!\N--Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! The chore boys\Nare fighting on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gawking for?!\NStop them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That explosion earlier\Nwas you guys' doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they kick you out\Nof the navy after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we managed to\Navoid being kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to agree to work\Nfor free for 50 years, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being kicked out\Nwould've been much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Luffy Wreaks\NHavoc in Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manages a Baffling Escape\Nfrom Captain Smoker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means Luffy-san\Nheaded for the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, he's taken a big step\Ntoward realizing his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now fill you in\Non our current mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Whadya want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former Navy Captain Morgan is\Nto be sent to Navy Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to face a court martial for the\Ncrimes of military exploitation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the tormenting of civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His transfer and delivery to\NVice-Admiral Garp is today's mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rankless, low-status scum\Nwill kneel before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no getting around it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should get court-martialed\Nor whatever else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does get what he deserves and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest,\NI still respected him anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was my idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess he did take\Nthings too far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, do you think\Nthey'll execute him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's no getting\Naround that either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given how my dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Vice-Admiral Garp!\N--It's Garp the Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's Navy Headquarters\NVice-Admiral Garp the Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero of the seas who\Ntravels all over the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Admiral Garp! Thank you\Nfor coming all this way personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby deliver Morgan to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dad...\N--Stop, Helmeppo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Vice-Admiral Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been up for five days now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've been going for a\Nnew doughnut-eating record...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the lack of sleep and rest has\Ngotten me a bit drowsy at 842...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This geezer's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morgan! Vice-Admiral Garp is a\Nleading figure at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man. Cut the sleeping act.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and I'll hack this chore boy\Nup and feed him to the sharks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this!\NHelmeppo-san is your own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son?! I don't need a son!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want is freedom!\NHis life means nothing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll toss him into a pool\Nof blood if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load! Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target-- 16 degrees starboard!\NDistance-- 8,263! Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's dangerous!\N--What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't shoot! My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll cut you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop, chore boy!\N--Don't go against regulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Helmeppo-san is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool. Stirring up trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's much better than\Njust abandoning my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'll go capture him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Come back!\NThere's no way you can catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's either quite the fool, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the racket?\NI'm finally awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Admiral Garp! I thought\Nfor sure you'd been done in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Someone's been done in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see it because I was asleep!\NWho was wounded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! The world will\Nkneel down before me once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today marks the new start of\Nthe newly reborn Morgan Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Set our course to the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NI said set our course to the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have no part in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He covered for me after this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when getting kicked out of\Nthe navy would destroy his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's protecting me, regardless of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! I'm going to capture you!\NJust give up--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! Who do you\Nthink you're talkin' to, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a piece of\Nuseless scum do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you're told, and I'll make\Nthings nice for ya. So be quiet and--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, you pathetic insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd ever listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who decides how I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit getting the wrong idea!\NWhat can scum like you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You!\N--M-M-Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the navy forces,\NI'm going to capture you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic! Pathetic! Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a couple of insects do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in my way and I'll\Nchop you both into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it turned out this way\Nafter you came to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I've made up my mind!\NI've decided to live for my beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And if I die fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I die fighting for that,\Nthat's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna die that badly, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I've become a\Nnavy officer! But, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I do die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid idiot! Let Coby go! Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn insects\Naren't even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never show yourself to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someday I will surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my poor supervision!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing the prisoner to escape\Nis the biggest blunder of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After what's happened,\Nthese two will be kicked out for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What truly lost causes you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anyone anywhere\Nwould take you in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'd only burden everyone\Nif we turned you loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice.\NCome with me to Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Admiral! You're going to\Ntake them with you to Navy HQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run away,\Nnow's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have no intention\Nof letting you say no, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh, my.\NWhat an odd day this has been!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how we wound up heading\Nfor the Grand Line, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the day will come\Nwhen we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gentle song
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it there for us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a wave washed away\Nthat little sand castle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up at the passing\Nclouds with a sad smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find the world is full of enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold you in my arms forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Here we go! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Oh, this is a navy photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no ordinary guy in it!\NKnow who it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa, it's Coby!\N--Coby? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's gonna be a navy softener!\N--You mean "officer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about being careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coby-Meppo's Resolve!\NVice-Admiral Garp's Parental Affection"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
